Download from github

 $ git clone https://github.com/gipi/ContactsContactManager.git

DEPENDENCIES
------------

Compatibility package version 4: copy it from the SDK directory

 $ cp <android-sdk-linux_x86 path>/extras/android/compatibility/v4/android-support-v4.jar libs/

COMPILING
---------

Enter into the root directory of the project, create a local.properties file

 $ android update project -p .

and finally compile and install

 $ ant debug && ant installd
